'''Jim Mahfood''' is a comics artist most noted for his work for [[Marvel Comics]], as well as his own "Riot Grrls" comic.

He did a page of '[[Fringer/Legends|Fringer']] character portraits for the '[[Rogues Gallery]]' section in [[Star Wars Gamer 7|''Star Wars Gamer'' 7]]

